<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.2.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-GJzZqFGwb1QTTN6wy59ffF1BuGJpLSa9DkKMp0DgiMDm4iYMj70gZWKYbI706tWS" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/icon.png" type="image/png">

    <!-- Add icon library -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">  

    <title>RootCase</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!--Modal-->      
    <div class="modal hide fade" id="newsletter" tabindex="-1" role="dialog">
        <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title">A chance to win a phone case!</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p class="lead">
                        All you have to do is like our 
                        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/root.case/">post</a> and
                        tag 3 friends and follow us!
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!--Nav bar-->
    <% include templates/header.ejs %>

    <div class="jumbotron fade">
        <div class="h-100 row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr width="50%" class="hideElement">

    <!--Info-->
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="display-4 text-center fade">What special about RootCase?</h2>

        <div id="info1" class="fade mt-3 pt-3">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-8 text-left">
                    <h4>
                        A phone case that doesn’t pollute our space.
                    </h4>
                    <p class="lead">
                        Rootcase is a beautifully designed and eco-friendly alternative to 
                        traditional plastic phone cases. Unlike normal plastic phone cases, 
                        Rootcase is 100% biodegradable, meaning it will have no negative 
                        effect on the environment when it’s being disposed. By buying Rootcase,
                        you’re doing your part to secure a plastic-free future for our planet.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                    <img class="images" src="/img/recycle.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <div id="info2" class="clearfix fade pt-3 mt-3">
            <div class="row hideElement">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-8 text-left">
                    <h4>
                        Reduce your plastic output today.
                    </h4>
                    <p class="lead">
                        For many decades now, our species have created and littered the 
                        Earth with plastics that take multiple lifetimes to degrade. If 
                        we continue this pattern, the title “blue planet” will have to 
                        compete with one that reflects the large amounts of plastic deposits 
                        instead. That’s why it is crucial for us as individuals, to reduce 
                        the negative impact we have on our planet. A phone case is a good 
                        and easy start to an eco friendly lifestyle. It may be small, but it 
                        definitely has an impact on everything, just as the smallest organisms 
                        do. 
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                    <img class="images" src="/img/ecofriendly.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="info3" class="fade pt-3 mt-3">
            <div class="row hideElement">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-8 text-left">
                    <h4>
                        Made of recycled materials
                    </h4>
                    <p class="lead">
                        Our case was brought from the earth and it should be returned from 
                        the Earth. We use 100% compostable wheat as well as some TPU. Although 
                        we have not yet reached 100% biodegradable material, we believe that 
                        this is a considerable amount compared to other typical products.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                    <img class="images" src="/img/charity.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!--Carousel-->
        <div class="mt-3 pt-3">
            <h4 class="display-4">Photo Gallery</h2>
            <div id="carouselExampleInterval" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active" data-interval="10000">
                        <img src="/img/phones.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item" data-interval="2000">
                        <img src="/img/phones.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="/img/phones.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleInterval" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                </a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleInterval" role="button" data-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!--Contact-->
        <hr width="75%">
        <div id="contact" class="text-center hideElement">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                <div class="p-1"></div>
                <div class="p-1">
                    <h1>Got questions?</h1>
                    <p class="lead">
                        If you’ve got any questions about Rootcase feel free to send us a 
                        message through the contact button below. A member of our team will 
                        respond to you in under 24 hours.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/contact">
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-primary my-2 my-sm-0" type="submit" >Contact Us</button>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="p-1"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
 
    <% include templates/footer.ejs %>
    
    <!-- Optional JavaScript -->
    <!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.0.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.6/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-wHAiFfRlMFy6i5SRaxvfOCifBUQy1xHdJ/yoi7FRNXMRBu5WHdZYu1hA6ZOblgut" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.2.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-B0UglyR+jN6CkvvICOB2joaf5I4l3gm9GU6Hc1og6Ls7i6U/mkkaduKaBhlAXv9k" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <!-- Load React. -->
    <!-- Note: when deploying, replace "development.js" with "production.min.js". -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/react@16/umd/react.development.js" crossorigin></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/react-dom@16/umd/react-dom.development.js" crossorigin></script>

    <!--JS-->
    <script src="/js/index.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>